## Limitations
This report is limited by the availability of sources that may have inherent biases, either for or against the overturning of Roe v. Wade. Additionally, the complexity of legal interpretations and the diversity of public opinion mean that not all perspectives may be fully represented. Further research could include more recent data and a broader range of viewpoints to provide a more comprehensive analysis.